description: This Python script defines a function to fetch top Hacker News stories using an Agent class, and then creates and uses an Agent instance to retrieve and print these stories.

classes.name: Agent
classes.description: A class representing an agent that can perform tasks using tools and context.

methods.name: get_top_hackernews_stories
methods.description: Fetches the top stories from Hacker News, returning a JSON string of story details.
